data.description: Accepted Offer with Contingencies. Cute home four blocks from downtown and Western Oregon University makes for a great starter or college rental.  The original two bedroom cottage has a converted garage which is being used as a third bedroom with walk-in closet, storage room and utility area. This additional room has multi-purpose uses which could include a bedroom, home office, family room or possibly an ADU with separate entry.  Yard produces grapes, raspberries, blueberries, and figs.
